<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Bursary for Students with Disabilities (BSWD)</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="45afc0b2-7aeb-490f-b10f-910f8dcb4c50" >

    <p>At Ryerson, we believe that everyone should have access to education and financial assistance, free of any barriers.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>The Bursary for Students with Disabilities (BSWD) is funded by the Government of Ontario and is a component of OSAP. It is intended to help students with financial need meet their disability-related educational costs for specialized services without having to incur additional debt, and increase access to post-secondary education for students with disabilities.</p> 
<p>This bursary is open to full-time or part time students with a permanent or temporary disability. To be eligible for funding for disability-related costs, students must complete the following steps:</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#45afc0b2-7aeb-490f-b10f-910f8dcb4c50");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resAccordion section">
























 


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel-group accordion background-hidden" id="ce13c9b4-d794-42b0-949c-0dbf9d7d9b6a" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
			
				<div class="resAccordionControl" role="group" aria-label="Accordion Actions">
					<button class="resAccordionOpenAll">Open All</button> <button class="resAccordionCloseAll">Close All</button>
				</div>
				<script type="text/javascript">$(document).ready(function(){ initResAccordionControl("ce13c9b4-d794-42b0-949c-0dbf9d7d9b6a", true); });</script>
			
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1605296214694-step-1--determine-osap-eligibility" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#ce13c9b4-d794-42b0-949c-0dbf9d7d9b6a" href="#accordion-content-1605296214694-step-1--determine-osap-eligibility" aria-controls="accordion-content-1605296214694-step-1--determine-osap-eligibility" aria-expanded="false">
                            Step 1: Determine OSAP Eligibility
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1605296214694-step-1--determine-osap-eligibility" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1605296214694-step-1--determine-osap-eligibility">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1605296214694 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="03392baa-4362-4832-83dd-ed274643687d" >

    <p>The BSWD requires you to be eligible for either Full-Time or Part-Time OSAP funding. You will have to create an OSAP account (if you do not have one already), and complete an OSAP application form on the <a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/osap-ontario-student-assistance-program" target="_blank">OSAP website<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a>. You will also have to submit a <a href="https://osap.gov.on.ca/prodconsumption/groups/forms/documents/forms/prdr018620.pdf" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">PDF file</span>Disability Verification Form<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-file-pdf-o"></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a>. Students must have their OSAP confirmation of enrolment completed before being assessed for BSWD.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#03392baa-4362-4832-83dd-ed274643687d");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1605296232155-step-2--determine-eligibility-of-equipment-services" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#ce13c9b4-d794-42b0-949c-0dbf9d7d9b6a" href="#accordion-content-1605296232155-step-2--determine-eligibility-of-equipment-services" aria-controls="accordion-content-1605296232155-step-2--determine-eligibility-of-equipment-services" aria-expanded="false">
                            Step 2: Determine Eligibility of Equipment/Services
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1605296232155-step-2--determine-eligibility-of-equipment-services" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1605296232155-step-2--determine-eligibility-of-equipment-services">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1605296232155 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="2e05fdf4-20e9-411f-8912-b8416b9a0ec0" >

    <p>In addition to the OSAP Disability Verification Form, which confirms a permanent or temporary disability, supporting documentation recommending specific services and equipment is required. Contact your Student Accommodation Facilitator, or the <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/accommodations/contact/">Academic Accommodation Support office</a> if you have not been assigned a facilitator, to discuss your eligibility for specific items and services.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#2e05fdf4-20e9-411f-8912-b8416b9a0ec0");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1605296246620-step-3--complete-bswd-application-form" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#ce13c9b4-d794-42b0-949c-0dbf9d7d9b6a" href="#accordion-content-1605296246620-step-3--complete-bswd-application-form" aria-controls="accordion-content-1605296246620-step-3--complete-bswd-application-form" aria-expanded="false">
                            Step 3: Complete BSWD Application Form
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1605296246620-step-3--complete-bswd-application-form" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1605296246620-step-3--complete-bswd-application-form">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
