 <li>Invoices and/or order forms are not acceptable</li> 
 <li>Equipment/software receipts must be submitted within 30 days of receiving the bursary</li> 
 <li>Services receipts must be submitted no later than 30 days after the study period, with appropriate supplemental documentation</li> 
